  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068400/extras/90164dfd09a9a1a7c821640db1c8ff79.poster.avif?t=1771917553\" width=600 height=94 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068400/extras/90164dfd09a9a1a7c821640db1c8ff79.webm?t=1771917553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068400/extras/90164dfd09a9a1a7c821640db1c8ff79.mp4?t=1771917553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">What do you do when you're locked inside a video game with a crazed AI and some guns? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">You RUN and KILL...That's what you do!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">in the world of radiant cell, get ready to defend yourself as you wall run, shoot, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">slow down time, and of course grapple. Be prepared to quickly adapt to new enemies and </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">new environments in every level.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">This is a fast-paced, parkour, shooter with inspiration from games like Ghost Runner, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Titanfall and many more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068400/extras/e9afbe2ada4c70d57b19b16bf2177f06.poster.avif?t=1771917553\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068400/extras/e9afbe2ada4c70d57b19b16bf2177f06.webm?t=1771917553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068400/extras/e9afbe2ada4c70d57b19b16bf2177f06.mp4?t=1771917553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">This is an easy game to pick up and play but hard to master. There are many routes to take to </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">escape each level but not all of them will be the fastest. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">You will want to replay the levels multiple times until you find the best gun and the best route </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">to kill the most enemies in the fastest time!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068400/extras/90164dfd09a9a1a7c821640db1c8ff79.poster.avif?t=1771917553\" width=600 height=94 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068400/extras/90164dfd09a9a1a7c821640db1c8ff79.webm?t=1771917553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068400/extras/90164dfd09a9a1a7c821640db1c8ff79.mp4?t=1771917553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">What do you do when you're locked inside a video game with a crazed AI and some guns? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">You RUN and KILL...That's what you do!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">in the world of radiant cell, get ready to defend yourself as you wall run, shoot, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">slow down time, and of course grapple. Be prepared to quickly adapt to new enemies and </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">new environments in every level.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">This is a fast-paced, parkour, shooter with inspiration from games like Ghost Runner, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Titanfall and many more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068400/extras/e9afbe2ada4c70d57b19b16bf2177f06.poster.avif?t=1771917553\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068400/extras/e9afbe2ada4c70d57b19b16bf2177f06.webm?t=1771917553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068400/extras/e9afbe2ada4c70d57b19b16bf2177f06.mp4?t=1771917553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">This is an easy game to pick up and play but hard to master. There are many routes to take to </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">escape each level but not all of them will be the fastest. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">You will want to replay the levels multiple times until you find the best gun and the best route </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">to kill the most enemies in the fastest time!</p>",
